<p class="ayah 70-24" id="24" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْوَٲلِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their wealth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَقٌّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) a right</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّعْلُومٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">known,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>24<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
